vsIWZA">Phụng sứ Đại Thanh quốc, kinh Quảng Đông dương phận Tam Châu đường, ngộ cụ phong - 奉使大清國經廣東洋分三洲塘遇颶風</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/T%E1%BB%87-c%E1%BA%A9u-1/poem-tw2egnsMNYQ32ngMmJbGjw">Tệ cẩu 1 - 敝笱 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Th%E1%BA%A3o-tr%C3%B9ng-2/poem-r8_xrbpPSYJifE9ykGYieA">Thảo trùng 2 - 草蟲 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91i-n%C4%83ng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-H5s_djxQcWKh3qzW5QeJBA">Tối năng hành - 最能行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-vpkhTYu5I0Ga1J2slJa8Pw">Trường hận ca - 長恨歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/author-LhlsyQN9Bp8xEaFjAVEqow">Vương Kiều Loan</a>)<br></div>	</div>
